      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but my doctor is always so rushed and i dont really want to deal with the whole insurance/prescription mess again if i can help it. if i just do it slowly, like maybe i skip a dose of zoloft every other day while i start a small dose of the st johns wort, would that be okay? i just want to get off the pharma stuff.",
